# Version control
**/.git
**/.github
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# IDE / editor
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Build output
**/bin
**/obj

# Node
**/node_modules

# Tests (not needed in production image)
**/tests

# Documentation (not needed in production image)
**/*.md
**/LICENSE

# Environment and secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Tooling
**/tailwindcss-windows-x64.exe
**/.claude

# Docker (avoid recursive copy)
**/docker-compose.yml
**/Dockerfile

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
